name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 3/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. This is the dazed child: The crazed clown did what was done to them and crafted a child to call their own. Planted inside is the brain of a sloth from an alien farm of curiosities. Philosophers will ask themselves, as the creator of the dazed child, does it make the crazed clown the true child?
